data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem in the desirable Hempfield School District! With over 1,620 sq ft of living space, this property offers comfortable living for all. One of the standout features of this home is the large addition in the back, providing a second kitchen and bathroom. This versatile space can be tailored to your needs, whether used as an in-law suite, entertainment area, or home office. The possibilities are endless! Inside, you'll find two bedrooms on the first floor, and an additional bedroom on the second floor. This home is located in a peaceful neighborhood in West Hempfield Township, offering a quiet and serene atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this spacious property your own. Schedule a showing today and explore the potential this home has to offer!
